				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The order you write to PPUSCROLL is backwards from what you intend. (<strong>here</strong> it's Y first, then X.) Also, there will be visible corruption on-screen between the 3rd and 4th writes if you change fine X.<br /><br />If you don't change fine X, consider the faster PPUADDR-only method.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

